sources.title: House of Danger
sources.description: Title: House of Danger Summary: To protect a young woman's life, a man pretends to be her injured friend so he can investigate a murder and capture the killers. Directed by: Charles Hutchison Actors: Onslow Stevens, Janet Chandler, James Bush Production Company: Peerless Pictures Release Date: 10 November 1934 (USA) Aspect Ratio: 1.37 : 1 To protect a young woman's life, a man pretends to be her injured friend so he can investigate a murder and capture the killers.
